result.name: Tai Hing Roast Restaurant

reviews.text: Soggy oil fried rice noodles with beef. Steamed chicken with rice is actually steamed chicken wings with rice. This restaurant used to be much better.

Okay food for a moderate price. Not the cheapest place around but it is more fancy. Okay portion sizes. Limited seating for huge groups. Weekdays have free rice and drink with dish purchase. English menu. Octopus card accepted as well.
Acceptable price n good seating area.. fast service with helpful staff
Food are served faster and freshly cooked.
Delicious but not cheap

result.name: 太興燒味餐廳

reviews.text: 少去太興食飯，知道價錢唔平，午餐成 $60 個，真係愈黎愈貴。咁想坐好d 就預左貴少少都好，但就唔多好味道，仲差過大家樂大快活呢d，真係無乜機會有下次了。
叫凍飲少甜，侍應會同你講即係多冰，乜溝到冇味嘅茶等如少甜？咁我叫凍0水少甜冇咁嬲
早餐啲食物質素係幾好，價錢同其他餐廳差不多，坐位舒服，侍應有禮，但燒味貴咗啲，唔低。
我嘅首選連鎖茶餐廳。奶茶好飲，燒味好味，服務都唔錯
味道普通, 菜式選擇不多, 價錢比一般茶餐廳貴少許
